===Specifications=== *Powerful 1.7GHz dual-core processor boosts performance *Memory: 4GB (eMMC), 8MB (SPI) flash and 512MB (DDR3) RAM *Get ultimate Wi-Fi speeds-up to 2.53Gbps (1733+800Mbps) *Quad-Stream technology delivers Wi-Fi to multiple devices *Next generation Wave2 Wi-Fi - 160MHz, MU-MIMO, Quad-stream *Four high-performance external antennas deliver maximum range *Twin USB ports offer high-speed, USB storage-ready access :One USB 2.0 port on the back and one USB 3.0 port on the side
